Introduction This tutorial is introducing a few very basic alignment helpers for this framework.
Horizontal alignment Use the horizontal shortcut&hellip;
.. to display two items next to each other.
Blocks Use the block shortcut&hellip;
.. to bring two items into one block, for example to display them below each other in a horizontal layout.
Centering .. horizontally Use the center shortcut to display something horizontally centered. Centering .. horizontally and vertically Use the center-center shortcut to display something horizontally and vertically centered.
